{"text_id":230952,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigated"," the"," thermal"," stability"," of"," metallic"," single","-","walled"," carbon"," nanotubes"," (","SW","CNT","s",")"," using"," O","(","N",")"," tight","-","binding"," molecular"," dynamics"," simulations","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," arises"," from"," the"," importance"," of"," understanding"," the"," behavior"," of"," SW","CNT","s"," under"," extreme"," temperature"," conditions",","," which"," could"," potentially"," limit"," their"," application"," in"," numerous"," fields","."," ","\n\n","Our"," simulation"," study"," revealed"," that"," the"," melting"," temperature"," of"," SW","CNT","s"," is"," highly"," dependent"," on"," their"," diameter",","," with"," thinner"," nanotubes"," being"," more"," stable"," at"," higher"," temperatures","."," Additionally",","," our"," results"," suggest"," that"," the"," observed"," thermal"," stability"," behavior"," of"," SW","CNT","s"," is"," primarily"," due"," to"," the"," pre","-","melting"," mode"," of"," atomic"," vibrations",","," rather"," than"," the"," diffusion"," of"," individual"," atoms","."," ","\n\n","To"," perform"," the"," simulation"," study",","," we"," employed"," O","(","N",")"," tight","-","binding"," molecular"," dynamics",","," which"," is"," a"," computationally"," efficient"," method"," suitable"," for"," simulating"," large"," systems","."," We"," used"," a"," combination"," of"," classical"," molecular"," dynamics"," techniques"," and"," Lange","vin"," dynamics"," simulations"," to"," investigate"," the"," thermal"," stability"," of"," SW","CNT","s","."," ","\n\n","This"," study"," provides"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," thermal"," stability"," of"," SW","CNT","s"," under"," high","-","temperature"," conditions",","," which"," can"," have"," significant"," implications"," for"," their"," practical"," applications"," in"," materials"," science","."," The"," results"," suggest"," that"," thinner"," metallic"," SW","CNT","s"," may"," be"," more"," stable"," at"," extreme"," temperatures",","," indicating"," their"," potential"," for"," use"," in"," high","-","temperature"," applications","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}